snippet.title: SURPRISING FAMILIES IN NEED WITH BRAND NEW CARS!
snippet.description:
I've been living in Dubai for the last 12 years and want to give back to my community, so I've partnered with Hyundai to give away brand new cars to families in need. It's been a tough year for so many. These three winners are so deserving. 
By the way guys, I'll be giving away more cars on my Instagram page very soon! Stay tuned xx, Alex

Thank you to Hyundai Middle East & Africa and Hyundai UAE for helping us!
